text: Fin TV has increasingly become a harbor of dogma and lack of accountability. In the main it has lost its value. No names, as to quote Warren Buffett: "Praise by individual, criticize by category."

@KeithMcCullough is among the few that recognize that the equity risk premium is the lowest since 2007 today. This means equities are overpriced, period. Ten cuidado.... @dougkass @seabreezelp see my Saturday Barrons interview on the sizeable hurdle represented by rate rise.
